cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper deals with the problem of texture interpolation and synthesis using a neural network. The most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the paper deals with image processing and texture synthesis. The second likely category is cs.GR (Graphics) as the paper discusses texture brushing and texture dissolve, which are related to graphics. The third likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia) as the paper deals with image and texture processing. The fourth likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper proposes a neural network-based solution. The fifth likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper discusses the training and evaluation of a neural network.
